BBQ Pulled Pork Burger

310 min
$15
650 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Description

Tender pulled pork slathered in smoky BBQ sauce, served on a soft bun with coleslaw for a perfect bite.

Ingredients

  • pulled pork: 2 cups
  • bbq sauce: 1 cup
  • hamburger buns: 4
